subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Kevin Anderson, who ended the 4-hour-18-minute match with a shutout in the fourth-set tiebreaker, reached the quarterfinals at a major for the first time, upending the third-seeded Murray.
